Package: msgtools
Type: Package
Title: Tools for developing diagnostic messages
Description: This package implements a number utilities for developing and maintaining error, warning, and other messages in R packages, including checking for consistency across messages, spell-checking messages, and building message translations into various languages.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2014-08-11
